The crunch match comes amid anticipation about Prince Harry's tell-all memoir, expected to be published this year. This has prompted conversations about the the distance between Harry and William. Their relationship was deeply affected by Harry's decision to step down from senior royal duties and move across the Atlantic in 2020, with Harry telling talk show host Oprah Winfrey in 2020 that the relationship was "space, at the moment". When the book was announced, Harry, 37, stated that it would be an accurate and wholly truthful depiction of his life, however, it is unclear how much he will discuss his brother in the memoir. With the Queen's Platinum Jubilee on the horizon, the brother's are coming under increasing pressure to iron out their differences and reconcile for the sake of their grandmother. FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES.... 